data.description: Welcome Home! Beautiful 2 bed / 1.5 bath 2 story in West Hamilton. Right across from the stunning St. Peter in Chains school. This home features beautiful woodwork throughout, updated flooring (LVP kitchen/dining, nice carpet in bedrooms/living room, tile bathrooms); Gilkey double hung insulated windows; finished basement (with unfinished utl. room); and lovely wood fireplace! Outside boasts a strong deck with new decking boards/railings; as well as detached garage and carport. Schedule a showing today and don't miss this great home!
